<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Verification Code</title>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Your Verification Code</h1>
  <p>Hello {{userName}},</p>
  <p>Your verification code is:</p>
  <p style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 8px; text-align: center; padding: 20px; background-color: #f5f5f5; border-radius: 8px;">
    {{code}}
  </p>
  <p>This code expires in {{expiresIn}}.</p>
  <p>If you did not request this code, please secure your account immediately.</p>
</body>
</html>
